  <description><![CDATA[<p class="p1">The ground floor of the Hotel Gardesana has recently been refurbished in a smart, modern style. It is situated only 100m from San Nicolo Harbour with its impressive array of boats and a pleasant 15 minute lakeside stroll to the historic centre of Riva. There is a bus stop close by and together with the ferries running from the centre of Riva, it is a great base to explore Lake Garda. There is a good size pool in the hotel’s garden with sunbeds and umbrellas to help you relax.</p>]]></description>
